{"tid":2256680,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"諸神聯誼會","createTime":"2020-10-24T14:13:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T01:53:11.000Z","uid":254452,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bca29cc79148ec6d44a7c8ae46cf284e20d402e0","tid":2256680,"uid":254452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T14:13:29.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><span class=\"x-large\">當頭棒喝</span></p><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zF4ALcc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzF4ALcc.jpg&h=cf6ba533&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在世界樹之嶺的庭園裡,諸神舉辦了千年一次的聯誼會,這次的舉辦人奧丁熱情地與眾神打開話匣。<br />\n<br />\n奧丁對佛陀說:「世上對我們已沒甚麼具挑戰性的事,若不可娶妻生子,太沒趣了吧!」<br />\n<br />\n佛陀微笑不語。<br />\n<br />\n奧丁續說:「你看你的好友耶穌,聽說他也娶妻生了兩個兒子啦。」<br />\n<br />\n耶穌打從心底裡高興的笑了笑:「怎及你厲害啦!生了九個子女。」<br />\n<br />\n奧丁滿意地點頭,對自己的能力很驕傲,顧盼眾神,無一敢與他相比。<br />\n<br />\n忽爾,天上一時有大火柱掠過,一時又降下傾盆大雨。<br />\n<br />\n「奇怪!這是甚麼異象?」眾神既驚且疑,急急擋住。<br />\n<br />\n大雨持續約半分鐘,然後一個魁梧俊美的身影降下。<br />\n<br />\n「好久不見,濕婆!我們開始了很久,還以為你不來了!」奧丁熱情地擁抱濕婆。<br />\n<br />\n「真的很抱歉!因為我與太太做愛太過投入,眨眼就做了一百年。一年前我猛然想起今天的聯誼會,已盡快把林伽拔出趕過來,好在也不算太遲,也管不著剛才一邊噴發一邊趕來,幸好沒有在大家面前失禮。」<br />\n<br />\n濕婆雙手合什,謙謙有禮作賠罪狀,奧丁一邊帶點疑惑地抹乾身上的水漏,一邊合什回禮。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong>寓意: 一個人有能力是掩蓋不住的,你總有機會像直接顏射般令別人對你另眼相看。</strong></span>"},{"pid":"4ef9300ac8077aff5341ba3060873a32ab27ddc7","tid":2256680,"uid":254452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T14:15:15.000Z","msg":"FB 達文西西  <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E9%81%94%E6%96%87%E8%A5%BF%E8%A5%BF-104528784764320/?view_public_for=104528784764320\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E9%2581%2594%25E6%2596%2587%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E8%25A5%25BF-104528784764320%2F%3Fview_public_for%3D104528784764320&d=ob16Qiumsg8bXj4Ev1LzLAy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=73da0252\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E9%81%94%E6%96%87%E8%A5%BF%E8%A5%BF-104528784764320/?view_public_for=104528784764320</a>"},{"pid":"15c9f71de47cd9402e1ec5ca5aedb6ac17c1c006","tid":2256680,"uid":254452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T15:54:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bac05d11a007164235657a5728b6496254a82d64","tid":2256680,"uid":254452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T16:10:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65493b5b61982d5012b6dca1da18a8b175a2f0de","tid":2256680,"uid":254452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T01:53:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}